org.assertj.swing.data

Class TableCellInSelectedRow

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.assertj.swing.data.TableCellInSelectedRow
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TableCellFinder

    public class TableCellInSelectedRow
extends Object
implements TableCellFinder

    Looks up a cell in the first selected row of a JTable.

    Example: 

     // import static org.assertj.swing.data.TableCellInSelectedRow.selectedRow;
 JTableCellFixture cell = window.table("records").cell(selectedRow().column(2));
    Author:
    Alex Ruiz
